•	HIGH QUALITY REMOVABLE MATTE* VINYL: I only use the highest quality vinyl. It has the look of being painted on but without the mess and expense.
•	DIE CUT not printed, so they do not have a background (clear or otherwise). The wall or surface you apply the decal to will be the background. A Die-Cut decal is a die-cut shape made from one of the many awesome colors shown in my color swatch.

•	I recommend installation to smooth, semi-gloss or gloss enamel paint. Avoid matte finish Latex paints and paints that contain anti-graffiti agents or stain blockers as well as Low VOC or VOC free paints, sand paints and suede paints.
